    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need new brakes and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable entry into this model who doesn't mind doing a little bit of work.",
